[[classpath">
== Apache Ant classpath
[[classpath_setting">
=== Setting the Ant classpath
		
			Ant allows to create classpath containers and use them in
			tasks. The
			following
			`build.xml`
			from a project called
			_de.vogella.build.ant.classpath_
			demonstrates this.
		
		
[source,xml]
----
include::res/classpath/build.xml[]
----
		

[[classpath_print">
=== Print
		You can
			use
			the following statements to write the full classpath
			to the
			console. You can
			use this to
			easily verify if the classpath is
			correct.
		
		
			<programlisting>
				<xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"
					parse="text" href="./examples/classpath/classpath.txt[]
----
		

